Now, we define the `Fact` statement and prove it.

```tactics
lemma MeasureTheory.ringHaarChar_adeles_isOneOnUnits :
  ∀ x : (𝔸 ℚ)ˣ, ringHaarChar x = 1 := by
  intro x
  rw [ringHaarChar_adeles_rat x]
  rw [prod_eq_one_iff_of_nonempty]
  · -- show each factor is 1
    intro p
    -- infinite place
    cases p with
    | infinite =>
      simp [infinite]
      rw [ringHaarChar_infinite]
      simp
    | finite v =>
      simp [v]
      rw [ringHaarChar_finite]
      simp
  · -- show the product is nonempty
    use Rat.infinitePlace
    simp
```

